    • Constructor Detail

      • NamedEntity

        public NamedEntity(java.lang.String name,
           java.lang.String type,
           int startIndex,
           int endIndex)
        Creates the structure of a Named Entity with its name, tag and its length, so its startIndex and endIndex.
        Parameters:
        name - This is the concrete name of a Named Entity.
        type - This is the Named Entity tag.
        startIndex - This designates at which word in a sentence the Named Entity begins.
        endIndex - This designates at which word in a sentence the Named Entity ends.
